For the salad, place the bulgar wheat in a large bowl. Pour over enough boiling water to cover and then cover with foil. Leave to rest for 10 minutes to steam.Add the raisins, orange juice and a squeeze of lime juice and stir together.Add the hemp seeds, red onion, chilli powder and soy sauce and cover with foil again until ready to serve.For the poussin, half-fill a pan with water. Add the garlic cloves and mixed herbs. Bring to a simmer and place a steamer on top.Place the poussin breasts into the steamer, cover with a lid and steam for 6-8 minutes, or until the poussin is cooked through.To serve, spoon the bulgar wheat salad onto a warm plate and place the steamed poussin on top.